## Third-Party Software and Acknowledgments

OnWapp is built upon and incorporates the following open-source projects. We are grateful to their authors and contributors:

### Core Dependencies

**whatsmeow** - WhatsApp Web API library for Go
- Repository: https://github.com/tulir/whatsmeow
- License: Mozilla Public License 2.0 (MPL-2.0)
- Copyright: © Tulir Asokan
- OnWapp uses a fork at: https://github.com/felipyfgs/whatsmeow

**libsignal** - Signal Protocol implementation for Go
- Repository: https://go.mau.fi/libsignal
- License: GNU Affero General Public License v3.0 (AGPL-3.0)
- Copyright: © Tulir Asokan

### Web Framework

**Gin** - HTTP web framework for Go
- Repository: https://github.com/gin-gonic/gin
- License: MIT License
- Copyright: © Gin Contributors

### Database

**pgx** - PostgreSQL driver and toolkit for Go
- Repository: https://github.com/jackc/pgx
- License: MIT License
- Copyright: © Jack Christensen

**lib/pq** - Pure Go Postgres driver
- Repository: https://github.com/lib/pq
- License: MIT License

### Storage

**MinIO Go Client SDK**
- Repository: https://github.com/minio/minio-go
- License: Apache License 2.0
- Copyright: © MinIO, Inc.

### Messaging

**NATS Go Client**
- Repository: https://github.com/nats-io/nats.go
- License: Apache License 2.0
- Copyright: © NATS Authors

### Logging

**zerolog** - Zero allocation JSON logger
- Repository: https://github.com/rs/zerolog
- License: MIT License
- Copyright: © Olivier Poitrey

### Documentation

**Swaggo** - Swagger documentation generator
- Repository: https://github.com/swaggo/swag
- License: MIT License

### Utilities

**google/uuid** - UUID generation
- Repository: https://github.com/google/uuid
- License: BSD 3-Clause License
- Copyright: © Google Inc.

**godotenv** - Environment variable loader
- Repository: https://github.com/joho/godotenv
- License: MIT License

**go-qrcode** - QR code generator
- Repository: https://github.com/skip2/go-qrcode
- License: MIT License

### Protocol Buffers

**protobuf-go** - Go support for Protocol Buffers
- Repository: https://github.com/protocolbuffers/protobuf-go
- License: BSD 3-Clause License
- Copyright: © Google Inc.

